==English==

===Etymology===
The term was first used in the ''[[w:South Park|South Park]]'' episode "[[w:Chef Aid|Chef Aid]]", which originally aired on October 7, 1998, as the fourteenth episode of the second season.

===Noun Phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Chewbacca]] [[Defense]]'''

#''Criminal defense.'' A satirical term for any legal strategy or propaganda strategy that seeks to overwhelm its audience with nonsensical arguments, as a way of confusing the audience and drowning out legitimate opposing arguments.

